channel.title: CMD window when i open it in Moparscape
channel.description: Hello, i got this probelm when i open the CMD window and it says press any key is closes it and..can somone tell me how to get free items in Moparscape (sorry if i ask nooby questions but i am very NEW to Moparscape) :D

item.title: CMD window when i open it in Moparscape
item.dc:creator: @Agent766 Agent766
item.description:
@Agent766 wrote:

Go to Help ==> Item IDS and click next to the search thing. then type in what you want and get the item ID. Then in the game type ::pickup (ID) (Amount)
Ex.
::pickup 0773 1
